{"tid":905390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉非禮3女同事 律政司高級檢控官王永森大角嘴墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-11-17T05:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T07:29:25.000Z","uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"698d0d66af0610ba011aa9f038632cc1eff11b6f","tid":905390,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1366638/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1366638%2F&d=s3MI7VAOkm5bhBhmo8PddC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=14e32fd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1366638%2F&h=bfb160b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1366638/</a><br />\n本報得悉，涉嫌非禮3名女同事的律政司高級檢控官王永森，今早在大角嘴海帆道凱帆軒寓所墮樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n49歲王永森於本周三解東區裁判法院提堂，被控3罪於14年至今年4月期間先後在律政司俱樂部，7樓入口處和走廊，涉分別用手向3名女同事「掃背」，用腿撞臀部或用文件夾拍向胸部等猥褻行為，案件延至明年1月17日，王永森准以現金2000元保釋外出，但須要每月首天向旺角警署報到及不准接觸控方證人。<br />\n<br />\n事發於早上9時58分，一名中年男子在海帆道11號凱帆軒2座高處墮下，昏迷倒臥平台，當場證實死亡。警方在現場檢獲遺書，正聯絡死者家人了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n記者：徐曉伊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抑鬱症？"},{"pid":"ef2b489dab39da9f1ec5379239b28b55d775839f","tid":905390,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"「用腿撞臀部或用文件夾拍向胸部等猥褻行」<br />\n<br />\n用腳拍個胸，好似好高難道"},{"pid":"8aa81daaea17ced9f3a4004a975967d1c6523d3c","tid":905390,"uid":50744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef2b489dab39da9f1ec5379239b28b55d775839f","tid":905390,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"「用腿撞臀部或用文件夾拍向胸部等猥褻行」<br />\n<br />\n用腳拍個胸，好似好高難道"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"你走先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5774a334927